I'm excited to announce that my client has started publishing the articles we've been working on for the past few months: words and cover images by yours truly! 

I would love to hear everyone's thoughts on the pieces and any identified areas of improvement. They are a health technology brand that had zero content prior to my work with them, so all this is built from scratch.

Don't go easy on me though- I really want to improve my writing!) You can find the articles here: <https://www.kgoal.com/blogs/pelvic-health|https://www.kgoal.com/blogs/pelvic-health>
